description.narrative: The overall development objective (PDO) for this APL Program is to increase private investment in the Nigeria PPP infrastructure market and specifically the core infrastructure sectors. The development objective for Phase I is to establish effective institutionaland technical mechanisms and instruments for origination and development of PPP projects.
